➜vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版图赏：质感突出，诠释什么是「五彩斑斓的黑」
https://www.ifanr.com/1365880?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	32587
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365922" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sddsf.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="3375" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sddsf.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sddsf-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sddsf-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sddsf-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>熟悉时尚圈的朋友应该对亚历山大·王（Alexander Wang）不会陌生。作为当今最红最年轻的华裔设计师之一，他的品牌 alexanderwang 叫好又叫座。</p>
<p>在 2019 年 12 月 vivo X30 的发布会上，vivo 首次宣布与 alexanderwang 合作，推出 vivo X30 Pro AW 联名限定版，并于今年 2 月正式发售。vivo 也成为 aw 首个且迄今为止唯一一个合作的中国品牌。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365881" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ChMlWl57N3SIIwgPAADuahdfz_EAAN20APYZ9EAAO6C618.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="693" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ChMlWl57N3SIIwgPAADuahdfz_EAAN20APYZ9EAAO6C618.jpg 520w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ChMlWl57N3SIIwgPAADuahdfz_EAAN20APYZ9EAAO6C618-360x480.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 520px) 100vw, 520px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 亚历山大·王和 vivo X30 aw 定制版</p>
</div>
<p>时隔不到一年，vivo 再度牵手 alexanderwang，推出了 vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版。与上次不同，这次限量 1000 台，售完不补。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365884" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06259oo.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06259oo.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06259oo-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06259oo-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06259oo-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>作为限量发售的机型，每一台 vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版，都有一个专属编号，增添了一份仪式感。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365885" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06262-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06262-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06262-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06262-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06262-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>相比普通版，aw 联名版使用了全新的 CMF（Color Material Finishing）设计语言。机身以亚光黑色为主色调，背面依然采用了 AG 玻璃工艺，这种高级的蒙砂质感看上去有点像金属，但触感上比金属柔和不少。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365886" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06271-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06271-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06271-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06271-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06271-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>最吸睛的还属背部硕大的 Logo「wang」，这是 alexanderwang 的标志性符号。姓「王」的朋友，会有一种量身定做的感觉。</p>
<p>在观感上，「wang」的 Logo 并不「扎眼」，而是与深色的背面「相处」地十分融洽。这是因为在 Logo 的表面，蒙上了一层深锖色镀膜，增强了背部色彩的一体性，看起来深邃且神秘。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365887" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06272-01-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06272-01-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06272-01-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06272-01-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06272-01-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>由于采用了幻彩全息纹理的印刻工艺，所以通过不同角度光线的变化，可以看到不一样的色彩，可以说是「五彩斑斓的黑」了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365888" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/njn.gif" alt="" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/njn.gif 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/njn-360x203.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/njn-768x432.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>在手机背面的下方，还印刻了 vivo x alexanderwang 的标识，字体较小，且颜色与背景十分接近，因此不会显得背部信息过于繁杂。并且由于印刻是在表面玻璃之下进行的，所以摸上去并不会有凹凸的感觉。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_174721-01.jpg" alt="" width="2780" height="1848" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_174721-01.jpg 2780w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_174721-01-360x239.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_174721-01-768x511.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_174721-01-1024x681.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2780px) 100vw, 2780px" /></p>
<p>手机边框的颜色虽然也是深色，但明度比背面颜色要高，且磨砂质感更强，有点像钛金属的质感。电源键和音量加减键区域，做了抛光处理。电源键上还有凹凸不平的纹理，方便「盲操」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/hhh.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/hhh.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/hhh-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/hhh-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/hhh-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>顶部是一块玻璃，没有做 AG 处理，光泽感很强。玻璃之下印着「5G」的标识，以及「Professional Photography」，证明这台手机的影像功能不俗。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365891" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_175156-01.jpg" alt="" width="2708" height="1800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_175156-01.jpg 2708w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_175156-01-360x239.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_175156-01-768x510.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_175156-01-1024x681.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2708px) 100vw, 2708px" /></p>
<p>除了机身，alexanderwang 联名版的配件也做了特别定制，包装盒、充电器、数据线、耳机这些周边都以黑色为主色，这个跟普通版白色的配色不同。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365892" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06280-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06280-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06280-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06280-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06280-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>值得一提的是，卡针上也印有联名的信息，精致感十足，甚至可以作为一个小饰品放在皮夹包里。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365893" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nnn.jpg" alt="" width="2108" height="1404" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nnn.jpg 2108w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nnn-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nnn-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nnn-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2108px) 100vw, 2108px" /></p>
<p>提到黑色，我们不仅会联想到神秘、酷，还会将其与大胆、勇敢、不妥协等词语联系到一起。vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版或许是想表达黑色的不羁，将黑色由表及里地注入手机「灵魂」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365901" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06281e.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06281e.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06281e-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06281e-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06281e-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>vivo 为这款限定版手机，设计了 aw 定制专属主题。深色的壁纸和图标，让手机正面看上去非常简约、纯粹。不过美观程度上，个人觉得有些一般，看久了眼睛还会有些疲劳，尝鲜过后还是换用了其他主题。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365895" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/oooo.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/oooo.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/oooo-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/oooo-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/oooo-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>vivo 的 X50 系列，有一个很独特的设计，就是「双色云阶」。它通过梯级的形式对不同厚度的镜头进行分区，配色由上到下呈现从深到浅渐变。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365896" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06277-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06277-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06277-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06277-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/DSC06277-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>如此一来，就从视觉上缩减了手机顶部的单调感和厚度，不会让手机后背突起一个黑色的大方块，看上去更有秩序感和精致感。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365897" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ooo.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ooo.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ooo-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ooo-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ooo-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>当然，作为摄影旗舰，vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版的拍照表现令人满意。以下是该机的 JPEG 直出照片。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365903" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_205611.jpg" alt="" width="3264" height="2448" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_205611.jpg 3264w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_205611-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_205611-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_205611-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365904" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_184706.jpg" alt="" width="4080" height="3060" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_184706.jpg 4080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_184706-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_184706-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_184706-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4080px) 100vw, 4080px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365905" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_230830.jpg" alt="" width="4080" height="3060" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_230830.jpg 4080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_230830-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_230830-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_230830-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4080px) 100vw, 4080px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365906" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_212155.jpg" alt="" width="4080" height="3060" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_212155.jpg 4080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_212155-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_212155-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_212155-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4080px) 100vw, 4080px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365907" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_155405.jpg" alt="" width="3120" height="4160" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_155405.jpg 3120w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_155405-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_20200909_155405-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3120px) 100vw, 3120px" /></p>
<p>关于 vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版的硬件参数，这里就不展开赘述了，因为其硬件配置与普通版的 vivo X50 Pro+相同。感兴趣的话可以移步<a href="https://www.ifanr.com/1349476">爱范儿此前发过的相关评测文章</a>。</p>
<p>售价方面，vivo X50 Pro+ aw 联名限定版与普通版一致，12GB+256GB 售价为 5998 元。9 月 17 日 0 点开售。</p>
<p>​Alexander Wang 曾说，「任何人都可以打扮的光鲜亮丽，但个人品味流露于日常穿着」。如今的智能手机越来越精致，拥有不俗设计的手机拿在手里，足以当做日常配饰，彰显个人品味。</p>
