➜7.5 亿年前，你的家乡城市在哪里？
https://www.ifanr.com/1365641?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	36281
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365666" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu.png" alt="" width="1529" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu.png 1529w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu-1024x670.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1529px) 100vw, 1529px" /></p>
<p>天下大势，分久必合，合久必分。这个道理放在大陆板块的变化方面也合适。</p>
<p>据卫星定位测量，地球上每个大陆板块都在以每年五到六厘米的速度移动，或相互靠近，或者逐渐远离。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365672" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/aodaliyapiaoyi-1.gif" alt="" width="600" height="478" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/aodaliyapiaoyi-1.gif 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/aodaliyapiaoyi-1-360x287.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>按照科学家推算，很久远的时候，陆地是连在一起的，而后才逐渐分散形成如今的七大洲。如今，各大洲总体上又在逐渐靠近，总有一天会回到「整片」大陆的时代。</p>
<p>由 Christopher R. Project 提供地图，Ian Webster 开发的<strong> 3D 古地球地图</strong>，提供了可视化的视角，让我们能通过简单的触摸、点击、键盘输入等方式，查看远古时候的地球自然面貌，<strong>还能搜寻许多城市几千万年甚至几亿年之前在地球上的大致位置</strong>。</p>
<h3><strong>现在：看一眼这颗美丽星球</strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365671" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu10.gif" alt="" width="1572" height="986" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu10.gif 1572w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu10-360x226.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu10-768x482.gif 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu10-1024x642.gif 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1572px) 100vw, 1572px" /></p>
<p>用上帝视角观察现在的地球时，一种凄美、孤寂、渺小又温暖的感觉涌上心头。这，就是我们赖以生存的家园。</p>
<p>它是蓝、绿、黄、白四种颜色交织的球体，承载着无数的生命，<strong>这一方天地间，人类日复一日的重复着自己的爱恨情仇和生活的无关痛痒，追寻和算计着自身的利益，厌恶和逃避着烦恼、疾病和死亡</strong>。</p>
<p>我们能看到高耸的喜马拉雅山脉，也能一眼锁定「马里亚纳海沟」。赤道中部的岛屿犹如「被抛弃的孩子」，静静漂浮在海洋中，黄色的部分仿佛是地球的疤痕，诉说着「血肉」碰撞时的痛楚，顶端和底部的两大块白色区域显得如此神秘和危险，事实上早已成为「兵家必争之地」。</p>
<p>故事，就从拉萨开始吧。</p>
<h3><strong>2000 万年前：上海还在海下</strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365647" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2000wannianqian.png" alt="" width="1646" height="1162" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2000wannianqian.png 1646w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2000wannianqian-360x254.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2000wannianqian-768x542.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2000wannianqian-1024x723.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1646px) 100vw, 1646px" /></p>
<p>2000 万年前，陆地轮廓现在总体相差不大。澳大利亚，美洲、非洲、欧洲，地中海，阿拉伯半岛，南北极等地方看上去都很熟悉。</p>
<p>也有一些地方和现在的区别很大，比如上海还没有形成，海南岛和大陆仍保持着「亲密接触」，东南亚仍然是一块大陆，延伸到了赤道以北，马六甲海峡还没诞生。</p>
<p>位于青藏高原的拉萨，位置没有太大的变化，处在白茫茫的高原一片中，只是青藏高原的形状发生了较大的改变，从现在的一条白色鲸鱼，变成了一瓶「侧放着的酒瓶」。</p>
<p><strong>这一时期，早期的原始人已出现在非洲。</strong></p>
<h3><strong>3500 万年前：阿拉伯半岛还未离开非洲</strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365650" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian2.png" alt="" width="1510" height="1162" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian2.png 1510w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian2-360x277.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian2-768x591.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian2-1024x788.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1510px) 100vw, 1510px" /></p>
<p>来到  3500 万年前，拉萨出现在青藏高原的边缘地带，想必是一处半山腰的原始森林。</p>
<p>日本还和东亚大陆「若即若离」，保留着最后一些陆地的接壤状态。</p>
<p>最引人瞩目的是澳大利亚和阿拉伯半岛。一个离南极洲特别近，一个还是非洲的一部分。地中海还是一个可从大西洋通航印度洋的海洋，可直达印度西北部。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365651" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian3.png" alt="" width="1538" height="1180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian3.png 1538w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian3-360x276.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian3-768x589.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian3-1024x786.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1538px) 100vw, 1538px" /></p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365649" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian.png" alt="" width="1540" height="1158" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian.png 1540w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian-360x271.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian-768x577.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3500wannianqian-1024x770.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1540px) 100vw, 1540px" /></h3>
<h3><strong>5000 万年前：鲸鱼被逼「下海」</strong></h3>
<p>5000 万年前的大陆，估计会让很多人直呼看不懂了。</p>
<p>山东半岛和华北平原还是海洋，喜马拉雅山脉还是一条带状的高山，横跨了接近三个大洲的直线距离，拉萨处于一片汪洋泽国中，很有可能是一片气候适宜的海边地带，印度漂浮在海洋中，是一个独立的岛屿，整个美洲被海洋淹没了差不多一半，地球之肺亚马逊雨林还是海洋。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365652" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian.png" alt="" width="1356" height="1032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian.png 1356w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian-360x274.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian-768x584.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian-1024x779.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1356px) 100vw, 1356px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365653" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian2.png" alt="" width="1374" height="1030" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian2.png 1374w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian2-360x270.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian2-768x576.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/5000wannianqian2-1024x768.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1374px) 100vw, 1374px" /></p>
<p>海洋太强势，逼得不少陆地哺乳动物进化成海洋生物，例如<strong>现在最大的动物鲸鱼，科学家推测就是被逼「下海」的</strong>。</p>
<p>按目前公认的说法， 6600 万年前，小行星撞击了墨西哥的尤克坦半岛，这一事件导致恐龙大灭绝。</p>
<h3><strong>1.5 亿年前：南美刚和非洲「闹分家」</strong></h3>
<p>1.5 亿年前的大陆离得更近，南美洲和非洲紧紧靠在一起，北美洲和欧洲、非洲、南美洲都很近，物种从非洲跨海迁移到北美洲的难度应该不会很大。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365654" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian2.png" alt="" width="1532" height="1182" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian2.png 1532w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian2-360x278.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian2-768x593.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian2-1024x790.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1532px) 100vw, 1532px" /></p>
<p>澳大利亚和南极洲基本还是一个整体，南北极的冰川还不是太明显，欧洲「支离破碎」的地貌正在形成。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365656" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian3.png" alt="" width="1610" height="1168" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian3.png 1610w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian3-360x261.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian3-768x557.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian3-1024x743.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1610px) 100vw, 1610px" /></p>
<p>这个时期已经出现了最早的蜥蜴，原始的胎盘哺乳动物已进化，<strong>恐龙主宰着两个大陆</strong>。</p>
<p>拉萨在海岸线附近，临近赤道，说不定是一个远古版的深圳。</p>
<h3><strong>3 亿年前：拉萨在南极</strong></h3>
<p>时间来到 3 亿年前，拉萨还是一座南极城市。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365658" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian4.png" alt="" width="1396" height="1100" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian4.png 1396w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian4-360x284.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian4-768x605.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15000wannianqian4-1024x807.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1396px) 100vw, 1396px" /></p>
<p>这一期时期的大陆基本集中在南半球，且连在一起，我已经分不太清楚各个大洲和国家原始的位置了，只能借助软件的定位系统来大致判断城市所在。</p>
<p>北京在一座岛的边缘地带，伦敦在大陆的中心地带，是一座山脚下的内陆城市，华盛顿成了世界屋嵴，在雪线之上。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365675" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu4.gif" alt="" width="1468" height="1110" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu4.gif 1468w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu4-360x272.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu4-768x581.gif 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu4-1024x774.gif 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1468px) 100vw, 1468px" /></p>
<h3><strong>7.5 亿年前：海洋统治地球</strong></h3>
<p>古代地球最远可以查看 7.5 亿年前的地球，这时拉萨和众多城市一样，静静躺在海洋里，整个地球可能完全被海洋和冰川覆盖，<strong>生命的孕育才刚刚开始</strong>。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365676" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu2.gif" alt="" width="1468" height="1110" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu2.gif 1468w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu2-360x272.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu2-768x581.gif 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/diqiu2-1024x774.gif 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1468px) 100vw, 1468px" /></p>
<p>最后，出于好奇，我搜索了一下自己的家乡，没想到荆州这座城市 7.5 亿年前竟然在一座离北极很近的岛上。如今的一座内陆城市，算得上是 7.5 亿年前的格陵兰岛了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365660" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/75000wannianqian.png" alt="" width="1566" height="1192" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/75000wannianqian.png 1566w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/75000wannianqian-360x274.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/75000wannianqian-768x585.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/75000wannianqian-1024x779.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1566px) 100vw, 1566px" /></p>
<h3><strong>地球是奇迹还是异类</strong></h3>
<p>有天和朋友在散步，望着辽阔的天空，朋友突然幽幽蹦出一句话：想想其它星球挺惨的，孤零零的，没有生命，只有永远的死气沉沉。</p>
<p>不知道为什么我顺口就说出了一句话：<strong>不，你应该这样想，只有地球上有「虱子」，地球才是异类</strong>。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1365662" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/taiyangyundongtu.gif" alt="" width="497" height="261" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/taiyangyundongtu.gif 497w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/taiyangyundongtu-360x189.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 497px) 100vw, 497px" /></p>
<div class="editor-section-slice">
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 真实的太阳系运动图，地球的位置得天独厚，可以获得不少星球保护</p>
</div>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 辽阔的宇宙中，目前凭人类的科技所能观测到的宇宙范围，暂时还没有直接的证据证明有星球存在大量生命，地球能在如此空旷的宇宙中孕育出生命， 各种创造奇迹的条件缺一不可：有太阳在前面打头阵抗大型伤害，并且提供了生命必须的热量，有木星和它的卫星不断「吸引」着致命的陨石，最后还有月亮这个近卫贴身守护，挡住最后一波陨石「攻击」，创造地球的潮汐和四季。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">对于人类而言的，地球太宝贵了。<strong>如果哪一天地球彻底被我们「作」到不适宜居住，地球的自转和公转仍会继续，大陆仍会漂移，气候仍会变化，冰川仍会融化了又冰冻起来，海水仍会涨起来又退下去，只要太阳系和地球的运行保持稳定，新的物种仍会出现，地球根本不会 care 我们这个昙花一现的物种在它身上做过什么。</strong></span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">沧海桑田的变化中，剥离各种包装过的爱护地球的崇高理念，保护自然环境和物种的多样性，其实是在保护人类自己。</span></p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
<div style="overflow:hidden"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/zhuhai" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;"></a>
<div style="text-align:left;line-height:23px;margin-left:80px">
<div style="padding:10px 10px 10px 0">
<div style="margin:0;font-size: 14px;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/zhuhai" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;">朱 海</a></strong>
</div>
<div style="font-size: 13px; line-height:20px;">三流方案策划者，二流出镜主持人，一流败家浪荡侠</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align:right;border-top:1px dotted #ccc;padding:2px 10px; font-size:12px;">
